com.example.colibris.configuration

Class Me

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.colibris.configuration.Me

  • public class Me
extends java.lang.Object
    The Me class encompasses the information (mostly configuration information) concerning the device itself. Such information include the connexion graph, the calibration parameters (that are herein established)
